{"tid":796520,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大馬禁碧桂園項目    馬哈蒂爾上台前已形容項目「不是中國投資，而是殖民」","createTime":"2018-08-27T23:19:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-28T06:22:42.000Z","uid":35790,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9e9e731c0e06c4d032fcfc9cd6d2acd5e008e9aa","tid":796520,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T23:19:17.000Z","msg":"大馬禁碧桂園項目售盤外國客 馬哈蒂爾批非為大馬人而建<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">馬哈蒂爾上台前已形容項目「不是中國投資，而是殖民」，它與其他中資參與工程是納吉布政府將國家出賣給中國的證據。</span>當地大馬人除了抱怨有太多中國人在「森林城市」搶購單位外，還擔心其填海造地破壞環境和影響漁業。<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20180828/s00014/1535393579927\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180828%2Fs00014%2F1535393579927&d=gLXFOZz10GvIW1xai%2F2ACm6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=db671274\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180828%2Fs00014%2F1535393579927&h=61ad7db8\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20180828/s00014/1535393579927</a>"},{"pid":"57806bc56772d6493bde467b95e12c9a1de95ffc","tid":796520,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T23:24:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18d9f67aa5e511b08475cd5fa83e1faf39fe80c5","tid":796520,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T23:52:29.000Z","msg":"會唔會排中？"},{"pid":"b7c2876b8d98856d7b9f63a22c03d0cda53bc46d","tid":796520,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T23:53:43.000Z","msg":"醒覺了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7b4cd287f8dc0ce713261393db23cb28b92bfc8","tid":796520,"uid":153778,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"18d9f67aa5e511b08475cd5fa83e1faf39fe80c5","tid":796520,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"